snippet: “Just Tell Me That You Want Me” salutes Fleetwood Mac with 17 tracks by 17 artists, including Marianne Faithfull, the New Pornographers, Trixie Whitley and Best Coast.
abstract: Ben Ratliff reviews album Just Tell Me That You Want Me: A Tribute to Fleetwood Mac by various artists; Jon Caramanica reviews album The Whippoorwill by Blackberry Smoke; Nate Chinen reviews album II by Nude Beach.

byline.original: By BEN RATLIFF, JON CARAMANICA and NATE CHINEN

lead_paragraph: “Just Tell Me That You Want Me” salutes Fleetwood Mac with 17 tracks by 17 artists, including Marianne Faithfull, the New Pornographers, Trixie Whitley and Best Coast.

headline.seo: New Albums Include ‘A Tribute to Fleetwood Mac’
headline.main: 17 Takes on Legacy of a Band
